project1.title: Nutshells
project1.description: Nutshells is a new product offering that our team was tasked with building. It's a dashboard for people to use so they can organize their daily weather, events, articles, and chat messages all in one place.
project1.technologiesUsed: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Jquery, JSON, Promises, Bootstrap, Axios, Webpack, Firebase

project2.title: Developer Portal
project2.description: An app used to keep track of different items such as tutorials, blogs, podcasts, and resources. The user has the ability to add and delete items to each section. The app also utilizes the Github API to display the user's profile and their commits.
project2.technologiesUsed: React, Axios, Webpack, HTML, CSS, JS, Jquery, JSON, Bootstrap

project3.title: Zillodone
project3.description: An application that is used to help folks find home listings in their local areas. Users have the ability to view listings. They can also add listings, edit their listings, and remove them entirely.
project3.technologiesUsed: React, Axios, Webpack, HTML, CSS, JS, Jquery, JSON, Bootstrap
